data.description: Welcome to this charming 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath home located on a quiet dead-end street east of Tillamook. This delightful property offers a warm and inviting one level floorplan. Solid surface floors throughout the house, including the original hardwood. Freshly updated bathrooms are both bright and modern. New paint inside and out, ready for you to move in and make it your own.  The kitchen boasts new countertops, providing ample space for meal preparation and entertaining. Cozy Pellet stove & ductless heat pump for heating & cooling. New Hardi plank siding, gutters and downspouts. New septic in 2019.  Fenced backyard with a garden area, perfect for those with a green thumb or those simply seeking a place to relax and unwind. 2 car garage, workshop and storage building all add extra space!
